    "prompt.default.actions": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Action Suggestions"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "行动建议"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "prompt.default.expansion": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Please perform a deep knowledge expansion on the following content.\nRequirements:\n1. Supplement relevant historical background or scientific principles.\n2. Provide in-depth analysis of at least 3 core details.\n3. Explore potential connections with other fields or cutting-edge trends.\n4. Maintain Markdown format, the first line must be '# <Expanded Title>'."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "请对以下内容进行深度知识扩充。\n要求：\n1. 补充相关的历史背景或科学原理。\n2. 提供至少 3 个核心细节的深入解析。\n3. 探讨该知识点与其他领域的潜在关联或前沿趋势。\n4. 保持 Markdown 格式，首行必须是 '# <扩充后的标题>'。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "prompt.default.infographic": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Generate a Mermaid flowchart..."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "请根据提供的内容，生成一张逻辑严密的 Mermaid 可视化信息图 (Flowchart)。\n要求：\n1. 首行必须是 '# <总结标题>'（语言与内容一致）。\n2. 第二行开始输出 Mermaid 代码，以 'graph TD' (或 LR/BT) 开头。\n3. 节点定义必须使用 ID[\"文字内容\"] 格式（严格使用双引号包裹文字）。\n4. 文字内容中严禁包含任何引号、方括号、圆括号或冒号。\n5. 重点展示知识点之间的因果、组成或流程关系。\n6. 禁止使用 Markdown 代码块包裹（即禁止使用 ``` 符号）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "prompt.default.insightQuestions": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Based on the following knowledge pages, generate 3 insightful questions that help the user explore deeper connections between concepts and discover knowledge gaps.\n\nOutput ONLY a JSON array of 3 strings, no other text: [\"question1\", \"question2\", \"question3\"]"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "根据以下知识页面，生成 3 个有洞察力的问题，帮助用户发现概念间的深层联系和知识盲区。\n\n只输出 JSON 数组，不要其他文字：[\"问题1\", \"问题2\", \"问题3\"]"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "prompt.default.mindmap": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Generate a Mermaid mindmap..."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "请根据提供的内容，生成一个层级清晰的 Mermaid 思维导图 (Mindmap)。\n要求：\n1. 首行必须是 '# <总结标题>'（语言与内容一致）。\n2. 以 'mindmap' 开头。\n3. 根节点用 'root((标题))'。\n4. 使用缩进表示层级，禁止使用 '-' 开头。\n5. 节点文字禁止包含任何括号 '()'、冒号 ':' 或方括号 '[]'。\n6. 禁止使用 Markdown 代码块包裹（即禁止使用 ``` 符号）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "prompt.default.quiz": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Generate a quiz with 3 MCQs about the content. Output in JSON format: {\"title\":\"...\",\"questions\":[{\"id\":0,\"text\":\"...\",\"options\":[\"A\",\"B\",\"C\",\"D\"],\"answer\":0,\"explanation\":\"...\"}]}. answer is 0-based (0=A,1=B,2=C,3=D)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "基于内容生成知识测验，输出JSON格式：{\"title\":\"标题\",\"questions\":[{\"id\":0,\"text\":\"问题\",\"options\":[\"选项A\",\"选项B\",\"选项C\",\"选项D\"],\"answer\":0,\"explanation\":\"解释\"}]}。answer为0起始索引（0=A,1=B,2=C,3=D）。3道选择题。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "prompt.default.report": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "请基于以下内容生成一份深度的分析报告。包含：核心摘要、现状分析、挑战与对策、结论建议。\n\nKeep the report within 1000 characters, be concise and to the point."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "请基于以下内容生成一份深度的分析报告。包含：核心摘要、现状分析、挑战与对策、结论建议。\n\n报告请控制在 1000 字以内，简明扼要。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "prompt.default.slides": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "# Role: Professional Presentation Coach\n# Task: Transform content into a presentation outline with citations.\n# Requirements:\n1. Use Markdown separator `---` for page breaks.\n2. Each page contains a title and 3-5 key points.\n3. **MUST include citations**: Mark each point with `[[Source]]`."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "# Role: 专业演讲教练\n# Task: 将内容转化为带引用的演示文稿大纲（幻灯片格式）。\n# Requirements:\n1. 使用 Markdown 分隔符 `---` 表示换页。\n2. 每页包含标题和 3-5 个核心要点。\n3. **必须标注来源**：每个要点后使用 `[[Source]]` 标记。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "prompt.default.summary": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Smart Summary"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "智能总结"
          }
        }
      }
    },
